    "body": "## PR Description\r\nATT, add local_window support in Hopper FAv3 and unittests.\r\n* Local masking is checked in each mainloop iteration. It's possible to further optimize it by only checking local masking in the first m and last n iterations, and leaving iterations in-between unchecked. This PR doesn't do this optimization to make code easier to read. \r\n* This support is only added to fp16 / bf16 for now. fp8 support will be in separate PRs.\r\n\r\n## Tests\r\nAdded unittest for local attention.\r\n`python3.9 -m pytest -q -s test_flash_attn.py` passed.\r\n\r\nBenchmark: `python3.9 benchmark_attn.py`\r\nNo perf difference before v.s. after.\r\n",
    "created_at": "2024-09-16T23:00:34Z",
